			<div class="content" id="post-content-4779266">
									

<p>I'm of two minds about this.</p>
<p>I really dig the underlying notion, actually. And this is one of those rare cases where I think we can reverse the script and say a J might work better as a main-lister. Especially if you're just going to go ahead and bring pataphysics into this and destroy that 4th wall.</p>
<p>In general, as a -J, this kind of overstays its welcome. While I found myself smirking, I didn't really actually feel &quot;jokey&quot; until the leg cramp at the end.</p>
<p>I know it's tough to do much with this feedback, but it's my thoughts none-the-less. Consider restructuring this into a mainlister!</p>

